### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Health
### ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Auth — testes de autenticacao
### ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Sem auth → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "document": "12345678000190", "name": "Teste Auth" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 100, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### Bearer valido → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "document": "12345678000190", "name": "Teste Bearer" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 100, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### X-API-Key valido → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{token}}

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "document": "12345678000190", "name": "Teste X-API-Key" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 100, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### Bearer invalido → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer fake_key_invalida

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "document": "12345678000190", "name": "Teste" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 100, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

