### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### POST /api/v0/faturas — Processamento real
### ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Venda real (encaminha ao n8n) — com idempotency
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "customer": {
    "type": "PJ",
    "document": "12345678000190",
    "name": "Startup ABC Ltda",
    "trade_name": "Startup ABC",
    "email": "financeiro@startup.com",
    "mobile": "(11) 99999-8888"
  },
  "operations": [
    {
      "service": {
        "code": "CONSULT-01",
        "description": "Consultoria em gestao financeira",
        "price": 2500.00
      },
      "sale": {
        "amount": 2500.00,
        "due_date": "2026-05-15",
        "description": "Parcela unica"
      }
    }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Erros esperados
### ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Payload invalido → 422 (campo obrigatorio faltando)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "name": "Sem documento" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 100, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### Amount zero → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v0/faturas?dry_run=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customer": { "type": "PJ", "document": "12345678000190", "name": "Teste" },
  "operations": [
    { "service": { "code": "T1", "description": "Teste" }, "sale": { "amount": 0, "due_date": "2026-12-01" } }
  ],
  "payment_method": "BOLETO_BANCARIO"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Outros endpoints (v1)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar clientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar faturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/faturas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar cobrancas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cobrancas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### OpenAPI spec (JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

### Docs (Scalar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs
